<%- include("partials/header", { title: "About Us" }) %>

<div class="card">
    <h1 class="accent-text text-center">About attend.io</h1>
    <div class="mt-2">
        <p class="lead"><strong>attend.io</strong> is a next-generation attendance management solution designed specifically for academic excellence and institutional efficiency.</p>
        
        <div class="flex-gap mt-2" style="align-items: flex-start;">
            <div class="flex-1">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>We aim to eliminate the friction of traditional attendance tracking. By providing a seamless, role-based platform, we empower educators to focus on teaching and students to focus on their learning journey.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
                <h3>Technological Edge</h3>
                <p>Built on a robust Node.js and Express architecture, our system ensures high availability and resilient data management through optimized JSON storage and modular controllers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-2">
            <h3 class="accent-text">Core Features</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i> <strong>Real-time Tracking:</strong> Instant attendance marking and verification.</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i> <strong>Role-Based Access:</strong> Secure, customized views for teachers and students.</li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i> <strong>Advanced Analytics:</strong> Data-driven insights into attendance patterns.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="text-center mt-2 mb-2">
    <a href="/" class="no-decoration"><button class="btn-secondary">Back to Home</button></a>
</div>

